枚举类 AngleType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<AngleType>
com.shapeville.model.AngleType
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Comparable<AngleType>, Constable
public enum AngleType extends Enum<AngleType>
Enumerates the different types of angles for the angle recognition task. Each enum constant represents a specific angle type with a user-friendly display name.

  • 枚举常量概要

    枚举常量
    枚举常量
    说明
    ACUTE
    Angle greater than 0 and less than 90 degrees.
    FULL_ROTATION
    Angle exactly 360 degrees.
    OBTUSE
    Angle greater than 90 and less than 180 degrees.
    REFLEX
    Angle greater than 180 and less than 360 degrees.
    RIGHT
    Angle exactly 90 degrees.
    STRAIGHT
    Angle exactly 180 degrees.
    UNKNOWN
    Represents an unknown or unclassified angle type.
    ZERO
    Angle exactly 0 degrees.
